ce/Kenneth_C._Griffin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenneth_C._Griffin\"}, {\"begin\": 806, \"end\": 821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Citadel Securities\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"founder\", \"from\": 717, \"to\": 724}, {\"ngram\": \"a company\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 755}, {\"ngram\": \"the track and field events\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 798}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also saw breakthrough athletes likeL\\u00e9on Marchand, Summer McIntosh, and Pan Zhanle, \\\"swimmers I had never heard of before and most people had never heard of,\\\" gain confidence as they competed and smashed records, he told interns.\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 876, \"end\": 891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Summer McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"breakthrough athletes\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"Marchand\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 874}, {\"ngram\": \"Pan Zhanle\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 907}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 918}, {\"ngram\": \"most people\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"records\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1036}, {\"ngram\": \"interns\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McIntosh, 17, became the first Canadian to win three gold medals in a single Olympics.\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1056, \"end\": 1064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"score\": 0.9999999999979536, \"rank\": 2.0293824228826767e-12, \"text\": \"McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/McIntosh_Laboratory\"}, {\"begin\": 1087, \"end\": 1095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.940189966709714, \"rank\": 0.06358680266380083, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three gold medals\", \"from\": 1103, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"a single Olympics\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Pan, 20, broke his own record as he took home gold in the men's 100-meter freestyle.\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1143, \"end\": 1148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9964754047656645, \"rank\": 0.003339610616916169, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his own record\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1180}, {\"ngram\": \"home gold\", \"from\": 1192, \"to\": 1201}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 100-meter freestyle\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Marchand, the 22-year-old Frenchman, set four records in Paris.\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1240, \"end\": 1248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 0.9999915815253296, \"rank\": 7.68757823720423e-06, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"}, {\"begin\": 1297, \"end\": 1302, \"title